Wilson, a co-founder of The Beach Boys, has denounced a performance of Beach Boys music at the Safari Club International Convention in Reno, Nev.
The concert is being led by The Beach Boys’ co-founder, lead singer and chief lyricist Mike Love.
Wilson, a co-founder of The Beach Boys, has denounced a performance of Beach Boys music at the Safari Club International Convention in Reno, Nev.
The concert is being led by The Beach Boys’ co-founder, lead singer and chief lyricist Mike Love.
He then pointed to a Change.org petition that calls for a boycott of Beach Boys’ music until the performance is canceled.